  "id": 56,
  "title": "#56 - the time skip",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "July 22nd"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Hey I'm skipping ahead. The past week I am not going to write about :) if you want to know what happened you will have to come ask me in person or on the phone one day hehe."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But briefly there was"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "A motorcycle",
        "My birthday (wooo). It was fun.",
        "A week of epic adventures in Genova and two nights at Lake Como."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I just entered the alps biking from Lake Como."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I woke up early in lake Como. I was staying in a spare room that a couple had in their apartment building. I bought them wine for letting me stay there. How I found this room is another story. The short story is I met more nice people."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I woke up at 5:40 AM then biked around lake como. It was a really pleasant ride the whole time."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After I got 30 km in I took the option to take a small ferry to speed up my journey on the lake. It was 5 euros and I got a boat ride on the lake which was awesome."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Then I finally entered the Italian Switzerland Alps. It's soooo pretty."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I just biked and biked. There is a trail that follows the river that is 100 km long without cars!"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Fantastic."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In the evening i got some pizza and relaxed. I quickly went back to the trail and found a place to sleep off the trail."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "That's all for the 22nd (and the little parts of the time skip)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
